Rem ************************************
Rem *** Variables globales ***
Rem ************************************
Global G_Position_X,G_Position_Y,Image_ID

Rem --- Initialisation
G_Position_X = 100
G_Position_Y = 100
Image_ID = 1

Screen Open 0,320,200,16,Lowres
Curs Off
Flash Off
Cls 0

Rem --- Transparence
Colour 0,$FAA

Rem --- Charger la palette de la banque Object Editor
Get Sprite Palette 0
Rem 0 = banque Object Editor contenant ton BOB

Rem ************************************
Rem *** Boucle du jeu ***
Rem ************************************
Do
    P_CLAVIER
    P_UPDATE_BOB
    Wait Vbl
Loop

Rem ************************************
Rem *** Proc√©dures du programme ***
Rem ************************************
Procedure P_CLAVIER
   If Key State(76) : Dec G_Position_Y
   Else If Key State(77) : Inc G_Position_Y
   Else If Key State(79) : Dec G_Position_X : Image_ID = 1
   Else If Key State(78) : Inc G_Position_X : Image_ID = 0
   Else If Key State(69) : End
   End If
End Proc

Procedure P_UPDATE_BOB
   Bob 1,G_Position_X,G_Position_Y,Image_ID
End Proc
